version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-07-05
abstract: >
  Verilume is an open-source, local-first AI assistant for
  retrieval-augmented generation (RAG), hybrid web search,
  multimodal document understanding, and transparent source attribution.
  It combines local knowledge bases with trusted web retrieval to provide
  accurate, explainable, and privacy-conscious AI assistance.
